Coding of key variables

#make Sample and StimSet factors for lm
dat1$Sample <- factor(dat1$Sample, labels=c("Online", "Student"))
dat1$StimSet <- factor(dat1$StimSet,labels=c("Animal_House", "Furniture_Painting"))

#creating the factor variable Gender
dat1$Gender = factor(dat1$Gender_F1_M2_O3_, labels=c("Woman", "Man", "OtherNonBinary", "Missing"))

#removing data from participants who do not identify as women or men
dat1<-subset(dat1, Gender_F1_M2_O3_ <3)

#Scale variables (coefficients are standardized)

#scale continuous vars

#IVs
dat1$CESDnumScore<-scale(dat1$CESDnumScore)
dat1$PAQnumScore<-scale(dat1$PAQnumScore)
dat1$TAS20numScore<-scale(dat1$TAS20numScore)
dat1$AQnumScore<-scale(dat1$AQnumScore)

#DVs
dat1$ValPropCorrect<-scale(dat1$ValPropCorrect)
dat1$EmoPropCorrect<-scale(dat1$EmoPropCorrect)
